name: Ballet of dreams white frame
description:
A young girl born into unfortunate circumstances, Helen is a quiet but pleasant kid who has dreams of one day becoming a famous dancer. Her family doesn’t seem to support her dream and as it stands, she hasn’t been able to land a single successful audition anywhere. She refuses to give up though, her thoughts about her dream becoming more and more intense as she devotes every waking moment to finding success, maybe too intense even.

-----


The Gallery Gehenna Project is a daily art project where there are multiple frames for each individual artwork, each with different types of rarity applied. White frames will initially only be available via giveaways on twitter and discord. All artworks will be compatible within the Gallery Gehenna Game with each artwork unlocking a playable story segment.
